4eDySvAw&oe=69BE388D"}},"is_early_access_review":false,"score":5,"review_description":"Taiko Frenzy is a fantastic Taiko rhythm game that truly captures the power and spirit of Japanese drumming. The gameplay offers great variety, from striking the drumhead to hitting the rim, rapid sequences, and rhythm changes that keep each track engaging. The execution is flawless and highly precise\u2014you almost feel like a real taiko drum is right in front of you.\n\nThe environments are beautiful and immersive, perfectly matching the intensity and flow of the music. The progression system is especially rewarding, with unlockable drum skins, new sticks, different drums, and adorable charms for your bachi that you\u2019ll absolutely want to collect. The mix of traditional and modern music styles adds strong replayability and keeps sessions fresh.\n\nThis is a true hidden gem that somehow flew under the radar for far too long. If you enjoy rhythm games or want an authentic, energetic drumming experience in VR, Taiko Frenzy is a must-discover.","review_title":"\ud83e\udd41 Thunderous Rhythm with Authentic Soul","date":1765996207,"translated_review_title":null,"translated_review_description":null,"translated_developer_response_body":null,"developer_response":null,"review_helpful_count":9,"review_rank_by_viewer":null,"reported_by_viewer":false,"__typename":"QualityRating"},"cursor":"AQHSlRO-MSnznFHd8zxERgNuHRb_lAQQzAaN2hwxx7SXhQ1VdhjrtaoHlpKjnFOPcO0Zc5pahmRGfsR24R0LyO-64A"},{"node":{"id":"1047716361754443","author":{"id":"992820633910683","alias":"MetaMikMode","name":null,"smallIcon":{"uri":"https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/499303788_1009848965541183_4506481440971236217_n.webp?stp=c0.0.1080.1080a_dst-webp_s32x32&_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=BDnbNSETIoUQ7kNvwHsgNon&_nc_oc=Adnag5xkPxeTmy5TXHhQoHImYOLnXQg2x6wldL8ay-JmOtybc7GZYZ6IK6L3VcNB9LE&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_ss=8&oh=00_AfwoGBXkjnRWGJffsplnJcPVAfBBYuDNWGlaeUI6as8Zbw&oe=69BE54D2"},"mo